  introText="Play <strong>free 3D browser games</strong> with full 3D graphics — right in your browser. Chess with a rotatable board, IPL-style cricket, and a 3D platformer, all running smoothly on desktop and mobile with no downloads."
  seoHeading="Play Free 3D Games in Your Browser"
  seoText="Weekly Arcade pushes what's possible in browser gaming with full 3D experiences. Using WebGL and modern rendering, these games deliver console-quality visuals directly in your web browser — no plugins, no downloads."
  seoBullets={[
    '<strong>3D Chess</strong> — Rotatable board, smart AI, and 4 difficulty levels',
    '<strong>3D Cricket</strong> — Full IPL-style match with batting, bowling, toss, and super over',
    '<strong>3D Platformer</strong> — Latch, swing, and collect Sparks in Lumble',
